Login
	If you have an account on the system already, this will
	log you in with your username and password.

Register a new account
	This will let you create an account, claim a username,
	and set a password.

Connect as a guest
	Logs you into the system with no username.  Please note
	that many features may be restricted from guests for security reasons.

Get help for this menu
	Explain each of the five options.

Disconnect
	Leave without logging in.
